404,Prudential,"Activity throughout 2020 Work to quantify and model the nature of our climate risk exposure has continued throughout 2020, consistent with our strategic focus on climate change risk and in alignment with the TCFD recommendations.",2020.0
405,Prudential,The Group Risk and Group Actuarial functions have led efforts to deepen understanding of the exposure to climate-related risks in our asset management and asset owner businesses across the Group.,2020.0
