830,PingAn_12,"Measures of Ping An in practicing green building are as follow: （a) Improve energy efficiency by rationalizing the layout and adopting thermal insulation materials to maintain the office temperature, and reducing the use of air conditioners; reduce energy consumption by applying intelligent power supply systems, inductive lighting, energy- saving lamps, solar water heating systems and making full use of natural lighting; reduce water consumption by recycling rainwater and applying water-saving devices.",2020.0
