933,PingAn_3,"In particular, after controlling for emissions and firm characteristics, we find the following (Table 8): • The Weighted Average Cost of Capital (WACC) is in general lower with greater TCFD compliance (both composite indicators) and disclosure of Water/Land use and Location of physical risks.",2020.0
