956,PingAn_3,"Al- though understanding whether and how ESG compliance might affect firm value is notoriously difficult17, both em- pirically and theoretically, our findings provide support for the role that climate disclosures can impact the cost of capital dimension of broader corporate valuation frame- works (see Cornell and Damodaran, 2020, for example).",2020.0
