1629,PingAn_5,"2 Themes of climate disclosures based on unsupervised learning In order to discover unique themes covered by companies in their climate disclosures, we adopt an unsupervised learning approach – the Latent Dirichlet Allocation (LDA) model to extract “latent” topics from all the company reports in our sample (Blei et.",2020.0
1630,PingAn_5,"In total, we identiﬁed six themes including: (1) energy usage, (2) governance, (3) human rights and employee health and safety, (4) climate related risk management, (5) emissions, and (6) GRI reporting and materiality.",2020.0
