1641,PingAn_5,"3 Coverage of climate-related metrics To further shed light on the diﬀerent kinds of climate-related metrics covered, we examined the percentage of companies that disclose the four recommended climate-related metrics and their associated risks including emission, energy, water use, and land use.",2020.0
1642,PingAn_5,"Across all sectors, emission (92 percent) are energy (91 percent) are well covered by companies, whereas water (58 percent) is moderately covered and land use (6 percent) has the least coverage, possibly because the latter is only relevant for selected sectors (Figure 7).",2020.0
