1788,NipponLife,"Initiatives to Conserve Energy at Sales Offices In July 2018, the newly built Yuki Sales Office of the Nippon Life Oyama Branch became the first Nippon Life sales office to obtain the ZEB Ready*1 certification, the highest BELS*2 ranking.",2020.0
