2214,AXA_2,"AXA Climate can also better guide customers in their choices, better protect the crops required for global food security “and in doing so switch from the role of a parametric insurance provider to a partner in climate risk intelligence for the agriculture and the food industries,” concludes Antoine Denoix.",2019.0
