3217,TokioMarine,"Accordingly, as an initiative for contributing to the attainment of these goals, in November 2017 Tokio Marine Asset Management established the Tokio Marine Low-Carbon Japanese Equity Fund comprised of equities of Japanese companies actively working to reduce greenhouse gases.",2018.0
