3245,TokioMarine,"There is a concern for the growing natural disaster risk due to climate change, and Tokio Marine Group, working to resolve disaster issues and mitigate disaster damage, also gives due attention to the goal of the Paris Agreement and intends to contribute to its achievement.",2018.0
