3379,PingAn_2,"85 Responsible Investment Adhering to the United Nations Principles for Responsible Investment (UNPRI) and relevant guidelines issued by Chinese regulators, Ping An is the first company in China to sign the UNPRI, the Climate Action 100+ and the Green Investment Principles for the Belt and Road as an asset owner.",2020.0
