3548,TokioMarine,■ Provision of the Tokio Marine Japanese Equity Fund to Contribute to the Creation of a Low-Carbon Society Promoting initiatives toward realizing a low-carbon society is an urgent and important issue with the adoption of the United Nations Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs) and the Paris Agreement based on the goals set by the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change.,2019.0
