3929,AXA,"fr/les-principaux-resultats-de-lexercice-pilote-climatique-2020 AXA GROUP 2021 Climate Report 01 Cross interview: Denis Duverne and Thomas Buberl looking back and forging ahead On the occasion of the publication of AXA’s sixth Climate/TCFD report, AXA Group CEO Thomas Buberl and Chairman Denis Duverne exchange views on six years of climate action, as well as the challenges ahead.",2021.0
