4307,AXA,"Investigating today climate risks, including evolution of climate, exposure and vulnerability in the future, is critical for AXA, as a global (re)insurer, to support a sustainable growth, find innovative and preventive solutions for our clients worldwide and reinforce our role within society and communities at large.",2021.0
4308,AXA,"In order to tackle the complexity of climate risk modelling, we invest on the long-term on data collection, research and development at different time-horizon.",2021.0
